 is growing on native coral (Pocillopora spp.) and on sessile macroinvertebrate communities (Pinctada mazatlanica,\nMuricea appresa and Aplysina sp.) that are being aff ected by its invasion. This study must be taken into account by local\nand regional government authorities to create public policy programmes of monitoring for surveillance and control of\ninvasive species. These programmes should focus on integration of socio-economic and ecological eff ects. They should\nbe complemented by experimental design and analysis of environmental variables to provide technical information for a\nbaseline of bio-invasion analysis along the Ecuadorian coast and Gal\u00e1pagos, to avoid the expansion of invasive species\nnegatively aff ecting the marine biodiversity of mega-diverse countries such as Ecuador and other countries of South\nAmerica.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "C\u00e1rdenas-Calle, Maritza", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Perez-Correa, Julian", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Martinez, Priscila", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Keith, Inti", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rivera, Fernando", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cornejo, Matilde", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Torres, Genoveva Mu\u00f1oz", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Villamar, Francisco", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zambrano, R", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "C\u00e1rdenas, A", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Trivi\u00f1o, Miguel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Troccoli, Luis", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bigatti, Gregorio", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Coronel, Jorge", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mora, Elba", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Veitch, C R", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Clout, M N", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Martin, A R", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Russell, J C", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "West, C J", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 2", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Spe